</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="12.[212,1171,774,870]" pageId="12" pageNumber="1743">
Highly invasive species, pest of stored agricultural products (
<bibRefCitation author="Thomas AK &amp; Mc Donnell &amp; RJ &amp; Paine TD &amp; Harwood JD" box="[890,1103,814,838]" pageId="12" pageNumber="1743" refId="ref13993" refString="Thomas AK, Mc Donnell RJ, Paine TD, Harwood JD. 2010. A field guide to the slugs of Kentucky. Lexington (Kentucky): University of Kentucky College of Agriculture- Agriculture Experiment Station Publication SR- 103." type="journal volume" year="2010">Thomas et al. 2010</bibRefCitation>
). EA, NA, I.
</paragraph>
